text: Jackson Alexander Irvine (born 7 March 1993) is an Australian soccer player. He plays for FC St. Pauli in the Bundesliga and for the Australia men's national soccer team. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1993 births Category:Australian men's soccer players Category:2018 FIFA World Cup players Category:2019 AFC Asian Cup players Category:2022 FIFA World Cup players
